{% from "partials/carousel.njk" import carousel %}

<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 md:px-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">New Barns</h1>

  <iframe class="h-[400px] w-full rounded-lg my-6" loading="lazy" src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=52.4052703,0.27634360000001834&z=16&output=embed" title="Map of New Barns"></iframe>
  <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/70">Note: map marker position is indicative only</p>

  <div class="prose-page mt-6">
    <p>
      New Barns is our largest site within the City. It currently has 58 tenants, and is located
      in New Barns Avenue next to the City cemetery behind the playing field. Most plots are of
      10 poles in area, although some have been divided into two plots of 5 poles.
      <a href="/info/#polemeasure">(What&rsquo;s a pole?)</a><br />
      Mains water is available on this site. Off-street parking in the corner of the recreation
      ground (accessible from High Barns) is permitted for plot holders provided a parking permit
      (obtainable from the Site reps) is displayed.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="my-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="aspect-video">
      <iframe class="h-full w-full rounded-lg" loading="lazy" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/53WZm-x7MqM" title="New Barns video" allowfullscreen></iframe>
